{% doc %}
  @prompt
    "Create a responsive promotional benefits section with three columns, each featuring an icon and text. The layout should include:
    
    First column: Delivery truck icon with a heart, heading 'Free Shipping on Orders $15+'
    Second column: Money bag icon with dollar sign and crown, heading 'Sign Up to Get Discounts'
    Third column: Calendar icon showing '30', heading 'Free & Easy Returns'
    
    Design requirements:
    
    Icons should be simple line drawings in dark navy blue
    All text in dark navy blue color
    Headings should be large, bold serif font, center-aligned
    Clean white background
    Equal spacing between columns
    Desktop: 3 columns side by side
    Mobile: Single column layout, stacked vertically with all three sections in one scrollable line
    
    Style: Modern, minimal, professional e-commerce aesthetic with ample whitespace", in mobile in should in same line, it shouldn't be scroolable to seee all benefits, add option to select icons , ad option to upload custom icons 
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

